{"tid":2295262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟咩人會掉D膠袋同膠飲管落海？","createTime":"2020-11-21T15:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:59:42.000Z","uid":104965,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef1178870f803885fc49bbde8a9ea3e24f35e25","tid":2295262,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"綠色和平日日叫人因為咁唔好再用塑膠飲管<br />\n<br />\n喂 我無諗過含完支飲管要比海龜同海豚含喎！<br />\n<br />\n諗住掉去垃圾桶就去堆填區啦<br />\n<br />\n究竟支飲管係我掉去垃圾桶去到堆填區中間<br />\n<br />\n有咩原因會令佢跌左去個海度？<br />\n<br />\n特登掉落海果班就告鳩佢啦<br />\n<br />\n正正常常係陸地上用膠飲管點會飛左去海底塞住海龜個嘴呢？<br />\n<br />\n有無綠色和平人士可以答到？<br />\n<br />\n答到又合理嘅話我12月全飲熱飲唔用飲管"},{"pid":"40ce3aea29c0217218488abff50ff0cf575404a8","tid":2295262,"uid":69742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180703/mobile/odn-20180703-0703_00176_034.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180703%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180703-0703_00176_034.html&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5rw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=5eb4567f\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180703/mobile/odn-20180703-0703_00176_034.html</a><br />\n用下Google"},{"pid":"d6e40e11bd54ff1a5ae4e06592702bb36c5643df","tid":2295262,"uid":69742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ce3aea29c0217218488abff50ff0cf575404a8","tid":2295262,"uid":69742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180703/mobile/odn-20180703-0703_00176_034.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180703%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180703-0703_00176_034.html&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5rw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=5eb4567f\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180703/mobile/odn-20180703-0703_00176_034.html</a><br />\n用下Google"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:4